skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: say good morning
des:
Use this skill to start each day right! Alexa will say good morning to you!

Not only will Alexa say "good morning," but she will say it in a variety of interesting ways. From sweet well-wishing to slightly humorous morning sentiments. This skill has a variety of "good morning" sayings to suit every situation!

To use, simply say, "Alexa open Say Good Morning!"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
